<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka kum sawt In ding lem tang ka ie,
 Kumsawt suongpi Krista chunga lem in;
 A hun laiin theihtawp in sang ka,
 Ka umna lei hi hung bei pai tana.

[V2]
 Kumsawt hinna In det Krista chu ka neita ie,
 Damlai huihpi leh tuipi hung kinawk mahleh;
 Krista zalin ei chuppha ta puona.

[V3]
 2. Aw enviel tie gamlui khawvel hi.
 Lungngaihna leh natna'n a dim zo tai;
 A chung ah lungmuonna um ta lo,
 Sietna huihpi a kinawk tak ziekin.

[V4]
 3. Aw sietna tuipi a hung lien tai,
 Zion chaten Insang lemto tai tiu;
 Thagau thiengtho hinna'n kithuom in,
 Hinna sangpen Insang chungnung ahii.</lyrics>
<title>Kumsawt Hinna In Det</title>
<author>Thangneikhup</author>
<hymn_number>288</hymn_number>
</song>